                    distribution of letters, as opposed to using 'Content here, content here', making it look like
                    readable English.
                </p>
                <p>Phản hồi &bull; 100 lượt thích &bull; <i class="fas fa-thumbs-up"></i></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
